show.title: Aval Varuvaala
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/tYe8RQ
show.description: Aditya Singhania is a wealthy yet lonely businessman, and Roohi Bhatia is a self-made woman who runs a food stall, battling broken relationships, a cruel daughter-in-law, and painful memories of past humiliation. Their paths cross through Aditya’s daughter, Taanvi, where a simple matchmaking attempt turns into a profound story. Aditya hides his true identity to see whether Roohi loves him for who he is or for his wealth. But for Roohi, this relationship goes far beyond love — on this journey, she also reunites with the daughter she lost five years ago.
